Project Summary

Project Information

Field Value
Name JavaClient
Description Client classes for communicating with a Tethys database server. Class dbxml.Client provides interfaces for querying, both via XQuery and a JSON specification that will be compiled to XQuery. Class dbxml.uploader permits the upload of new data into a Tethys server.
Homepage tethys.sdsu.edu
